---
title: Asian-Inspired Fried Chicken Tacos with Charred Corn and Pickled Cucumbers
description: Crunchy, crispy textures and sweet heat combine with a blend of Asian flavours to hit every note! Breaded chicken breasts, pan-fried to golden perfection, are thinly sliced and added to soft tortillas loaded with slaw, creamy charred corn and quick-pickled cucumbers. These loaded tacos will make this a taco night to remember!
